\pard\fi360\ql\qnatural

\fs22 \cf0 Version 1.0.2
\f1\b0\fs20  (Friday March 21, 2003) \'d0
\f3 \
\pard\li520\fi-160\ql\qnatural
\cf0 \'b7
\f1  Reliably connects to more IRC servers and faster.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  IRC commands. Twenty of the typical IRC commands have been implemented for those die-hard users. Here is the current list: me, msg, query, ame, amsg, dcc send, join, part, quit, say, nick, away, topic, mode \'b1v, mode \'b1o, server, disconnect, names, clear and kick.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Rudimentary plug-in support! Plug-ins can be installed in any of the library directories, preferably: 
\f5\i ~/Library/Application Support/Colloquy/PlugIns
\f1\i0 . Contact me for the plug-in software development kit. Try 
\f5\i /itunes
\f1\i0  in a room to test the basic iTunes plugin.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Added the French localization.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Fixed an issue when using an Azerty keyboard that prevented typing characters with circumflex and trema accents (e.g. \'99, \'94, \'90, \'95). This fix might apply to other keyboard layouts.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Connections are now saved in the Connection Manager during the first launch.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Hidden windows now stay in the Dock and Window menus.\

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Changing a connection nickname will query the Keychain for that nickname's password.\
\pard\fi360\ql\qnatural

\f2\b\fs22 \cf0 \
Version 1.0.1
\f1\b0\fs20  (Saturday March 15, 2003) \'d0
\f3 \
\pard\li520\fi-160\ql\qnatural
\cf0 \'b7
\f1  Fixed the toolbar configuration crashes (the most reported crash). \

\f3 \'b7
\f1  The Emoticon and Encoding toolbar items now honor the "Use Small Icons" toolbar setting. \

\f3 \'b7
\f1  The Connect toolbar item now opens the "New Connection" dialog when no connection is selected. \

\f3 \'b7
\f1  IRC command queue tweaks to make things "snappier". \

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Support for password protected servers. \

\f3 \'b7
\f1  Nicknames with special characters now get encoded and are saved properly. This fixes the "|" (pipe character) bug.\
